{"synckey":1601684536,"updated":[{"bookId":"26711904","bookmarkId":"26711904_11_2055-2098","createTime":1601247542,"range":"2055-2098","markText":"最成功的减肥，是瘦体重增加，脂肪减少；最失败的减肥，是脂肪没减多少，减掉的都是瘦体重。","type":1,"chapterUid":11},{"bookId":"26711904","bookmarkId":"26711904_9_1917-1980","chapterUid":9,"markText":"快速减肥时，身体中的两种物质会迅速减少，一个是糖原，一个是蛋白质。在糖原和蛋白质丢失的过程中，我们的身体伴随着丢失大量的水分。","range":"1917-1980","createTime":1601130014,"type":1},{"bookId":"26711904","bookmarkId":"26711904_8_683-711","chapterUid":8,"markText":"减肥不是减体重，减体重也不是减肥，只有减脂肪，才叫减肥。","range":"683-711","createTime":1601129196,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"NO.4 减肥，不看体重看什么？","chapterUid":11,"chapterIdx":11},{"title":"NO.2 一天瘦一斤，瘦下去的是什么？","chapterUid":9,"chapterIdx":9},{"title":"NO.1 减肥不等于减体重","chapterUid":8,"chapterIdx":8}],"book":{"bookId":"26711904","version":2129193913,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/50/YueWen_26711904/s_YueWen_26711904.jpg","title":"我的最后一本减肥书","author":"仰望尾迹云","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K57B79WG06^[M|D?IXt5oI","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#231d00"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#261d00"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#291d00"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#373204"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#393200"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#3b3200"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#4e481d"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#504900"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#524900"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#524a00"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#6a6212"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#6d6200"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#686130"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#877c00"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#827b47"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#867b00"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#9c9560"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#9f9643"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#a1961f"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#a49600"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#bcb03e"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#beb002"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#bfb100"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#d1ca90"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#d4cb74"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#dacc00"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#e8e4c2"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#f6e712"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#a1961f"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#bcb03e"},{"key":"3/100","